@node "_PCI_info" "Documentation de PCI.LDG"
@{0U}Que fait cette LDG ?                                              @{0}


Cette LDG (Librairies Dynamiques Gem) met … disposition les
43 fonctions que propose le PCI BIOS version 1.0


 @{0B}Attention:@{0} L'appel de ces fonctions doit se faire en mode
 superviseur. Seul la fonction get_pci_version() peut ˆtre
 appel‚ en mode utilisateur.


 ú @{0U}Liste des 43 fonctions PCI:@{0}

    1. @{"find_pci_device" LINK "_find_pci_device"}
    2. @{"find_pci_classcode" LINK "_find_pci_classcode"}
    3. @{"read_config_byte" LINK "_read_config_byte"}
    4. @{"read_config_word" LINK "_read_config_word"}
    5. @{"read_config_longword" LINK "_read_config_long"}
    6. @{"fast_read_config_byte" LINK "_fast_read_config_byte"}
    7. @{"fast_read_config_word" LINK "_fast_read_config_word"}
    8. @{"fast_read_config_longword" LINK "_fast_read_config_long"}
    9. @{"write_config_byte" LINK "_write_config_byte"}
   10. @{"write_config_word" LINK "_write_config_word"}
   11. @{"write_config_longword" LINK "_write_config_long"}
   12. @{"hook_interrupt" LINK "_hook_interrupt"}
   13. @{"unhook_interrupt" LINK "_unhook_interrupt"}
   14. @{"special_cycle" LINK "_special_cycle"}
   15. @{"get_routine" LINK "_get_routine"}
   16. @{"set_interrupt" LINK "_set_interrupt"}
   17. @{"get_resource" LINK "_get_resource"}
   18. @{"get_card_used" LINK "_get_card_used"}
   19. @{"set_card_used" LINK "_set_card_used"}
   20. @{"read_mem_byte" LINK "_read_mem_byte"}
   21. @{"read_mem_word" LINK "_read_mem_word"}
   22. @{"read_mem_longword" LINK "_read_mem_long"}
   23. @{"fast_read_mem_byte" LINK "_fast_read_mem_byte"}
   24. @{"fast_read_mem_word" LINK "_fast_read_mem_word"}
   25. @{"fast_read_mem_longword" LINK "_fast_read_mem_long"}
   26. @{"write_mem_byte" LINK "_write_mem_byte"}
   27. @{"write_mem_word" LINK "_write_mem_word"}
   28. @{"write_mem_longword" LINK "_write_mem_long"}
   29. @{"read_io_byte" LINK "_read_io_byte"}
   30. @{"read_io_word" LINK "_read_io_word"}
   31. @{"read_io_longword" LINK "_read_io_long"}
   32. @{"fast_read_io_byte" LINK "_fast_read_io_byte"}
   33. @{"fast_read_io_word" LINK "_fast_read_io_word"}
   34. @{"fast_read_io_longword" LINK "_fast_read_io_long"}
   35. @{"write_io_byte" LINK "_write_io_byte"}
   36. @{"write_io_word" LINK "_write_io_word"}
   37. @{"write_io_longword" LINK "_write_io_long"}
   38. @{"get_machine_id" LINK "_get_machine_id"}
   39. @{"get_pagesize" LINK "_get_pagesize"}
   40. @{"virt_to_bus" LINK "_virt_to_bus"}
   41. @{"bus_to_virt" LINK "_bus_to_virt"}
   42. @{"virt_to_phys" LINK "_virt_to_phys"}
   43. @{"phys_to_virt" LINK "_phys_to_virt"}


  Enfin, une derniŠre fonction vous renseigne le num‚ro de version
  du PCI Bios pr‚sent sur votre micro (ou un @{"message d'erreur" LINK "_PCI_ErrorCode"}).

   44. @{"get_pci_version" LINK "_get_pci_version"}


